[05/11/2019 14:49:48] <font color="#0000ff">(Disparo)</font>
[05/11/2019 14:50:04] <font color="#00ff00">¿Te han herido?</font>
[05/11/2019 14:50:08] <font color="#ffff00">(R E)</font>
[05/11/2019 14:50:28] <font color="#00ff00">Ese oro ya no me interesa.</font>
[05/11/2019 14:50:29] <font color="#00ff00">Me voy a México.</font>
